"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-lifestyle-paris-2024-olympics-spreading-love-with-condoms-but-no-champagne\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbLifestyle  Compiled byCarien Grobler  Deputy Digital Editor  3 minute read  4 June 2024  05:43 pm  In the romantic city of Paris, where pandemic-era Olympic restrictions have eased, the 2024 Games are fostering connections among athletes once more.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 128, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943061084, \"rank\": 5.693834775662222e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Approximately 300 000 condoms will be provided in the Olympic Village - nearly two per athlete for each day of the event.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 308, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving the keys,Sky Newsaccompanied Games officials on inspections of the Olympic Village, which will host 9 000 athletes in July.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the tour, they discovered an unexpected feature: the bed frames are made of sturdy cardboard, capable of supporting up to 250kg of Olympian weight.\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999997427987968, \"rank\": 2.2519854836470767e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dubbed \\\"anti-sex\\\" beds by organisers of the 2021 Tokyo Games, the cardboard-beds installed at the Olympic Village in Paris ahead of the 2024 games have generated quite a buzz.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943061084, \"rank\": 5.693834775662222e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it's essential to clarify that these beds were\\u00a0not\\u00a0specifically designed to discourage sexual activity.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, they were created with sustainability in mind.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Made from recyclable materials, including cardboard frames and mattresses, these beds aim to reduce environmental impact.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, organisers have ensured that 300 000 condoms will be available in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This renewed emphasis on international mingling contrasts with the social distancing measures in Tokyo and the previous intimacy ban imposed by the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999450051307, \"rank\": 3.147700056137608e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even in Tokyo, where athletes had to wear masks and sleep on the cardboard beds, 150 000 condoms were handed out, although organisers said that \\\"the distribution of condoms are to have athletes take them back to their home countries to raise awareness\\\".\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999450051307, \"rank\": 3.147700056137608e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laurent Michaud, the village director, emphasised the importance of creating a convivial atmosphere for athletes.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Collaborating with the athletes' commission, they aimed to establish welcoming spaces where athletes would feel enthusiastic and comfortable.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While a French staple will not be on the menu in the village, athletes will not go hungry.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.997662319928666, \"rank\": 0.0020045921380990976, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Michaud, \\\"No champagne in the village, of course, but they can have all the champagne they want also in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943061084, \"rank\": 5.693834775662222e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, the village will offer an extensive 350-metre buffet featuring world cuisine.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French specialties will also be available, prioritising athletes' nutritional needs and performance.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.997662319928666, \"rank\": 0.0020045921380990976, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Village, a \\u20ac2 billion (\\u00a31.7 billion) project, is primarily funded by property investors.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2350, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5358869573523506e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NOW READ:Italian minister's drug-taking tip: 'If you are gonna smoke a joint, do it right'  Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_cuisine\", \"score\": 0.9888952184052185, \"rank\": 0.010687147666032692, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_cuisine\"}, {\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9999991678915927, \"rank\": 6.898697946424588e-07, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Download our app  Get the latest news and updates on Whatsapp  The latest news directly in your inbox  Support Local Journalism  2026 The Citizen.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Whatsapp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re